# Build output. Especially obj/, which contains project.assets.json with
# absolute paths into the host's NuGet cache; copying it into the image
# breaks the "restore in one layer, publish in a later layer" pattern
# (NETSDK1064 "package was not found"), because --no-restore then reads
# host paths that don't exist inside the container.
bin/
obj/
out/

# IDE
.vs/
.idea/
*.user

# Local state
.env
*.tar
